casebody.data:
Robert Wayne HOLSEY, petitioner,
v.
Bruce CHATMAN, Warden. No. 14-7457 14A614. Supreme Court of the United States Dec. 9, 2014.

Opinion

Application for stay of execution of sentence of death presented to Justice THOMAS and by him referred to the Court denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Superior Court of Georgia, Butts County, denied.

Justice BREYERand Justice SOTOMAYORwould grant the application for stay of execution.
